{
  "stem": "1061.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was absolutely beside myself because here I was, all alone, left not knowing who was were.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother made-- I was skinny and I was-- you know, I looked very young.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Mother put rouge on me, and she stuffed-- she put something like-- something like a brassiere, to make me look that I was grown up, which I-- I was like a board, flat board.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was a child.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyhow, so I find myself here stuffed full of rags to fill me out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was very warm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The excitement, the dogs, the barking dogs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They would send the dogs on the people who wouldn't march in line.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They would shoot at anybody who didn't stay in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And of course, whoever couldn't walk, they-- forget it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then it was-- they were shot immediately.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyhow, soon after this march was over, which was horrendous, I found myself in a camp not far from that factory, that munitions factory.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not know that place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That place was once called-- was a firing range.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's why the Polish name for it is Strzelnica.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Strzelnica is a firing range, you see?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This Strzelnica was actually converted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was some barracks put in or whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or maybe there were barracks there before, but I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because this was not anymore in the town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- the community in which I lived had this industrial town and a bedroom town, you see?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The bedroom town where everybody lived was called Wierzbnik.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the big town, the industrial part where the factory was, was Starachowice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was really combined and named Starachowice, but everybody lived in the bedroom town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, this Strzelnica camp was very near the factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have never heard of it, I've never seen it, and I found myself completely alone.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I cried and I was petrified.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think the terror-- the real terror that gripped me in all my war-- war experiences, that was that point.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was of the greatest terror in my life because I was really alone, totally alone, for the first time in my life.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was only thanks to the people around me who comforted me, who-- who hugged me, who held me by my hand, and-- and don't cry, and your mother will come soon, and all this.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I was totally stricken with horror, with-- with fear.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, I have experienced fear after this point, too, you know, with the [? write-through. ?] After all, the war was already on for two years.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I have experienced enough fear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But nothing like that excruciating pain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, after everything settled down, I discovered that my father found himself in the same camp where I was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we also found out that there was another camp established around the area in a place called Majowka.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we found out subsequently that my two sisters, who were fin-- they were finally released after the town was evacuated-- cleared of Jews-- they found themselves in that other camp.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But meanwhile, we also discovered that people who did not go to either Majowka or Strzelnica camp were taken away to the railroad, loaded onto trains, and sent somewhere.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We did not know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But of course, now we know that this was Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at that point, there was talk about resettlement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, the euphemism forever being used that these people were going to work here in the factory, and the others were going to be resettled.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the trains that left that day where my mother with Mrs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Kazimerska ?] were among those, that went straight to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we know it for a fact now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, in Treblinka, there is-- you know, they have these jagged stones for each Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There is one big stone with a sign Starachowice, because we were, I think, among the early-- our town was among the early camp-- communities that was liquidated and sent to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very-- very soon.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll tell you why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because, you see, there were men and there were women, and every-- we were separated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But everybody, you know, found out who was among the men and who was among the women.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was-- of course, we didn't live in the same barracks but that didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You already-- I already saw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father, again, became a scribe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father was given-- he was typing up whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was typing their schedules, whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And most of these people were sent to work in the factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I worked in the munitions factory myself, but for a very short time because, subsequently, I was assigned to the laundry, to do laundry.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
